Industry: 
Building Materials, Plumbing Equipment


ITEM 4. INFORMATION ON THE COMPANY The Company Overview We are a Mexican company headquartered in Monterrey, Mexico, and our origin dates back to 1890. Our company was incorporated on May 30, 1936 and has a duration of 99 years. Our legal name is Fomento Económico Mexicano, S.A. de C.V., and in commercial contexts we frequently refer to ourselves as FEMSA. Our principal executive offices are located at General Anaya No. 601 Pte., Colonia Bella Vista, Monterrey, Nuevo León...
 Please check Mexican Economic Development Inc for more information.


















